Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.33,0:00:14.83,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}從進入結女開始 一直是一個人生活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.57,0:00:16.94,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.64,0:00:19.38,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哦 所以就…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.74,0:00:23.29,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是的 對不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.84,0:00:26.65,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}雖然有不想和瓜生在一起的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.06,0:00:29.75,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但還要打工和購物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.09,0:00:34.61,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}今天也是傍晚先確保了想買的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.05,0:00:38.54,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}而後為了買打折的商品 重新再來了一次
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.25,0:00:42.06,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}愛理 太見外了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.91,0:00:44.54,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼不能和我們說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.96,0:00:52.13,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我怎麼能說出口呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.89,0:00:00.89,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}

Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.89,0:00:00.89,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.34,0:02:31.54,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼能說出口 我可不想讓別人知道我的弱點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.92,0:02:38.02,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以我就會要拜拜不定是去自我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.50,0:02:43.86,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\pos(1095,580)}{\pos(980,560)}{\3c&HB58E00&}{\fn方正综艺_GBK\fs40\fad(500,300)}愛理的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.16,0:02:48.57,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一個人生活是由於我任性而開始的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.88,0:02:52.44,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}艱苦的生活也是早就有了覺悟的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.10,0:02:56.68,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是 結女的大家看來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.77,0:03:00.85,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我是學園長女兒的瀨名愛理
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.38,0:03:03.52,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我無法辜負她們對我的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.86,0:03:06.64,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不想讓她們知道我生活的艱辛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.12,0:03:09.67,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不希望她們知道我的弱點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.93,0:03:14.37,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我必須一直做著她們所期待的我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.44,0:03:20.51,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因為我是瀨名愛理
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.63,0:03:29.19,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有什麼可笑的 反正真相就是這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.25,0:03:30.01,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}太高興了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.28,0:03:36.81,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼呀 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.19,0:03:42.52,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因為 我從沒想過被瀨名背叛的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.70,0:03:43.15,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.36,0:03:44.03,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.12,0:03:44.54,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.62,0:03:45.28,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.53,0:03:52.27,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.04,0:04:09.75,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.61,0:04:12.80,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我從這個方向走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.68,0:04:15.38,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}現在還是在新市街呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.09,0:04:16.56,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.02,0:04:18.69,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}愛理住的公寓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.91,0:04:21.05,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.30,0:04:27.45,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是的 我可不管了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.89,0:04:30.89,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個 真的很小 也很舊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.37,0:04:32.64,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}做好覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.58,0:04:47.51,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}看起來挺寬敞的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.01,0:04:53.39,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}愛理整理得很好 都沒有安潔我顯身手的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.27,0:04:55.73,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只是沒有什麼傢具而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.35,0:04:57.06,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.15,0:05:02.72,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒關係嗎 讓我進來女孩子的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.71,0:05:06.77,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}都到這裡了 也不能叫你回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.23,0:05:10.58,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但要是做什麼多餘的事情 可是會把你趕出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.89,0:05:14.21,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那我就打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.89,0:05:16.39,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.62,0:05:21.97,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}家這麼小 真對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.66,0:05:23.36,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.23,0:05:30.08,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}說起來 提出要在愛理的家裡一起吃飯的是安潔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.52,0:05:32.92,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是的 也太突然了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.48,0:05:36.02,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是 為什麼大家都堆在這麼窄的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.56,0:05:39.30,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}安潔作為女僕 是理所當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.81,0:05:41.52,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}刨皮之類的 就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.35,0:05:43.66,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}然後就由我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.23,0:05:45.54,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要是有什麼需要幫忙的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.93,0:05:50.92,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這裡太狹小了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.63,0:05:58.17,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是 稍微有些其樂融融吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.80,0:05:59.36,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.42,0:06:01.20,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.10,0:06:05.94,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.80,0:06:19.24,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我開始吃了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.58,0:06:26.54,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.15,0:06:31.16,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這是櫻乃的蘿蔔 安潔醃制的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.38,0:06:32.77,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}加點料吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.48,0:06:38.97,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}更好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.85,0:06:41.96,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}能來愛理的家 真的是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.68,0:06:43.56,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}櫻乃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.96,0:06:45.64,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.54,0:06:47.23,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.91,0:06:51.55,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有件事一定要你們幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.18,0:06:52.86,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.13,0:06:57.32,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在學園 不要和人提起這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.10,0:06:59.07,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.90,0:07:00.62,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.85,0:07:02.20,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.32,0:07:05.07,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.55,0:07:09.61,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.69,0:07:31.01,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一起吃也可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.31,0:07:33.12,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}愛理
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.97,0:07:34.59,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.15,0:07:36.96,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}愛理 坐這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.91,0:07:44.75,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.36,0:07:48.77,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}紗凪 記得要幫我保守秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.09,0:07:49.75,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.05,0:07:50.54,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.96,0:07:54.01,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}椋梨也不是會到處亂說的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.51,0:07:56.14,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哦 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.48,0:08:01.30,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.71,0:08:04.15,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}全部都是捲心菜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.52,0:08:06.07,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這就是瀨名的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.36,0:08:08.10,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這是愛理的便當嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.70,0:08:10.13,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}捲心菜是很好的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.38,0:08:14.18,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}富含食用纖維 還有各種吃法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.17,0:08:17.22,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}難道說 這之前也一直是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.43,0:08:18.24,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.59,0:08:22.53,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以一直都一個人自己吃的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.14,0:08:25.19,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}給你煮蘑菇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.64,0:08:27.30,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}給你小塊炸鰹魚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.99,0:08:29.31,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}給你可樂餅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.21,0:08:33.86,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這麼豪華的便當 好久沒有見到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.49,0:08:35.44,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.18,0:08:37.30,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我開始吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.58,0:08:41.56,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要是不介意的話 今後也一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.64,0:08:47.36,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.73,0:08:59.88,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那我去學生會了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.34,0:09:00.98,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那再見
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.43,0:09:01.94,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.35,0:09:04.22,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}看起來很忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.81,0:09:07.02,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}兼任著兩邊的學生會嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.03,0:09:09.91,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個… 瓜生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.78,0:09:11.41,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.44,0:09:14.99,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我們也有什麼工作嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.28,0:09:18.61,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒 暫時這一段時間好像什麼都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.56,0:09:21.97,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}於是… 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.38,0:09:26.08,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我幫你復習的那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.33,0:09:29.50,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 真的會幫我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.80,0:09:30.35,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.15,0:09:32.79,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有這樣的約定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.10,0:09:38.58,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這之前作為工作交換條件 讓她幫我復習 算是有…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.63,0:09:39.91,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那可不叫算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.72,0:09:43.13,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我很明確地和你約定了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.40,0:09:46.20,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}考試前也沒有安排打工 時間上正好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.58,0:09:48.49,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.91,0:09:49.69,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那當然
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.38,0:09:52.49,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那我就恭敬不如從命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.15,0:09:54.25,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}承蒙您的關照了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.91,0:09:56.94,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那馬上從今天就開始可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.42,0:09:59.02,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}離考試還有一周的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.39,0:10:00.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.40,0:10:01.07,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.38,0:10:03.27,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還一周啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.74,0:10:06.04,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不會吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.59,0:10:08.81,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}地點就在我家可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.31,0:10:09.77,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.97,0:10:11.06,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.42,0:10:16.24,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在瀨名的房間 和我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.55,0:10:17.26,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.34,0:10:21.22,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.41,0:10:22.94,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}又不是只有兩個人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.56,0:10:24.84,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是的 櫻乃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.98,0:10:25.53,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.05,0:10:28.10,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我一起教櫻乃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.49,0:10:30.02,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}櫻乃 可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.37,0:10:32.84,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 幫了我大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.83,0:10:40.66,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}愛理 這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.22,0:10:46.61,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這個是 把這裡的方程用於剛才的數學公式中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.43,0:10:49.99,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.37,0:10:52.43,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這樣比較能放鬆嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.81,0:10:54.89,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒 不是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.63,0:10:57.43,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}愛理 很合適
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.71,0:10:59.57,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.41,0:11:02.53,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真的很合適的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.21,0:11:06.04,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那… 為什麼大家都來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.44,0:11:09.42,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}實習課上做了蛋糕 讓大家一起吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.95,0:11:13.05,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}黏著美羽前輩 不知不覺就…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.49,0:11:19.16,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}想著盡可能地照顧愛理
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.56,0:11:21.92,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是的 那算什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.77,0:11:26.42,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}大家一起學習的話 會更愉快的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.22,0:11:33.51,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}下次把小熊喵也帶來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.74,0:11:37.13,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這就饒了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.62,0:11:49.62,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}感覺變成不同的教室了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.33,0:11:52.45,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}都是愛理的影響
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.27,0:11:55.23,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.10,0:12:12.15,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}氣氛好很多了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.74,0:12:15.71,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.37,0:12:17.15,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.30,0:12:18.21,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.72,0:12:19.67,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}請拿好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.70,0:12:21.32,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好的 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.86,0:12:22.76,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.97,0:12:24.05,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.00,0:12:27.37,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我馬上就回來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.91,0:12:28.00,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}女僕咖啡DOLCE
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.91,0:12:28.00,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}新主人贈送一杯飲料
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.91,0:12:28.00,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}新女僕招募中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.77,0:12:29.50,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}OK 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.97,0:12:31.39,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.76,0:12:32.22,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.83,0:12:39.85,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}吃驚了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.78,0:12:44.07,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 嗯 超微有點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.59,0:12:49.60,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不覺得天羽前輩會去打工
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.14,0:12:51.01,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.39,0:12:54.15,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.68,0:13:01.01,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喵咪部沒有被承認是正式的社團
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.48,0:13:03.27,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒有運營的資金
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.27,0:13:07.84,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只有教室的使用被默許了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.25,0:13:11.84,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是 不要誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.32,0:13:15.96,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我邀請瓜生 不是為了這個目的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.00,0:13:19.66,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.01,0:13:23.27,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.34,0:13:24.92,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.13,0:13:31.81,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不準更靠近美羽前輩了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.14,0:13:35.38,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}乾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.76,0:13:40.20,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是的 果然對男人溫柔是最大的錯誤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.60,0:13:42.58,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}快點給我小時 垃圾蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.81,0:13:46.27,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}從美羽前輩身邊離開
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.34,0:13:47.44,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.55,0:13:53.86,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}總算揭開假面具了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.58,0:13:56.66,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}假面具?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.89,0:14:01.30,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}其實紗凪極度地厭惡男人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.97,0:14:05.32,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好像從試驗合併開始就在裝好孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.19,0:14:09.87,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.04,0:14:10.94,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.17,0:14:14.77,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}總算是趕上了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.83,0:14:17.70,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝 瀨名
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.20,0:14:22.43,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}大家是互相幫忙而已 我也該說謝謝的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.89,0:14:28.59,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.68,0:14:32.37,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.13,0:14:35.44,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼 發生什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.23,0:14:37.34,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}稍微等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.13,0:14:38.68,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.58,0:14:47.84,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}生日快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.77,0:14:52.21,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼會知道我生日
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.72,0:14:56.05,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我可是你的青梅竹馬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.74,0:14:58.37,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.44,0:15:02.17,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是… 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.47,0:15:07.69,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}讓大家給我慶祝 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.49,0:15:16.13,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就算和媽媽一起住的時候 也沒有慶祝過
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.56,0:15:19.97,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.11,0:15:21.85,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}瀨名
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.75,0:15:27.02,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我們想要慶祝你的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.46,0:15:40.16,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}即便這樣 也不可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.29,0:15:49.25,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不 沒有不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.95,0:15:58.65,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}恭喜你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.08,0:16:08.85,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.25,0:16:15.97,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}然後數天之後 期中考試結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.51,0:16:20.84,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}乾杯…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.96,0:16:26.08,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}總算結束了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.43,0:16:28.88,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}關鍵的考試回答得怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.32,0:16:29.95,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.11,0:16:34.99,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}多虧了你 比想象中的要好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.40,0:16:35.93,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.49,0:16:40.12,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 確實這是有剩餘時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.70,0:16:42.33,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這確實是有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.89,0:16:46.01,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}以前時間都是很緊張的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.62,0:16:49.59,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可能是各務台的大家來的原因吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.32,0:16:54.53,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}也就是說 各務台的學生沒有緊張感
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.97,0:16:56.13,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不不
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.56,0:16:59.34,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒有緊張感的只是瓜生而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.58,0:17:00.49,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.45,0:17:04.57,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}都是你 害得我都變鬆懈了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.21,0:17:06.38,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}確實有是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.16,0:17:31.48,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}總結會 還是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.30,0:17:35.31,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}很多的事情都開始在變化了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.34,0:17:39.89,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}大概是那傢伙來了之後開始的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.87,0:17:44.36,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}大家也是… 我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.91,0:17:48.15,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我可不想那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.64,0:17:52.42,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}太好了 你還留著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.33,0:17:55.91,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你不是回去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.89,0:17:58.48,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我忘記道謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.68,0:18:02.23,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}幫我復習考試 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.30,0:18:05.53,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為了說這個 特意回來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.80,0:18:07.22,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.47,0:18:14.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要不要兩個人再總結一次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.55,0:18:19.19,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這事情的起因 就是我們兩個人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.76,0:18:30.37,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}確實 你太顧慮他人了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.85,0:18:44.73,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以就在想 那傢伙到底是有多麼大局觀念的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.15,0:18:49.18,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你就這樣 馬上就笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.18,0:18:54.02,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要是覺得這樣就給人親切感 是大錯特錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.34,0:19:07.86,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.29,0:19:18.46,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好像 覺得很懷念的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.56,0:19:20.39,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.98,0:19:25.77,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}覺得發生了好多好多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.63,0:19:27.17,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.20,0:19:31.43,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是的 暴露了好多好多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.06,0:19:34.81,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 但我沒告訴任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.72,0:19:36.53,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.79,0:19:37.30,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.36,0:19:44.26,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我 一直認為自己生活上的情況會成為自己的弱點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.60,0:19:48.91,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是瓜生… 大家也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.95,0:19:54.26,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}都不把這個看成弱點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.39,0:19:58.85,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.11,0:20:03.08,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}很狡猾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.34,0:20:07.62,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因為我對此很是感激
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.53,0:20:10.63,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以 很狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.84,0:20:15.03,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誰都有弱點的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.92,0:20:17.18,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}當然我也有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.72,0:20:25.14,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是瓜生一直都顧慮著他人 顧慮著各種各樣的氣氛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.13,0:20:30.14,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我覺得那就是我的弱點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.36,0:20:35.06,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我這麼做 是為了我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.97,0:20:38.62,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}氣氛要是變壞了 我會很感到愈發厭煩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.77,0:20:39.64,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}忍受不住
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.22,0:20:54.50,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}瓜生要是不過分勞累就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.45,0:20:57.59,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以一直都這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.94,0:21:02.40,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只要笑出來 就不會和他人產生距離感
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.57,0:21:05.36,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這就是我的弱點
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.38,0:21:09.81,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以我們都是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.36,0:21:16.85,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝 瓜生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.93,0:21:18.76,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}瓜生?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.33,0:21:26.93,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 瀨名
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.85,0:21:30.57,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.08,0:21:36.06,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那再見
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.85,0:21:38.53,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 小心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.58,0:21:41.01,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}Byebye 瀨名
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.83,0:21:47.35,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}Byebye 瓜…生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.22,0:23:29.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 新吾先生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.16,0:23:31.03,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那是安潔的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.28,0:23:35.58,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn方正综艺_GBK\fs55\blur2\pos(640,564)\fad(500,500)}屬於你的女僕
